{"tid":1772221,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「世紀冤案」2019年，香港全部人都是林子健","createTime":"2019-12-06T12:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T07:02:22.000Z","uid":157483,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bd0eb55a5097a35218e835ba8f3bb9f6c8098dcc","tid":1772221,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:19:07.000Z","msg":"當年林子健被黑警屈，個個都信警察，全世界當佢傻仔 遺棄佢 唾棄佢 恥笑佢 <br />\n到2019年，大家先後知後覺睇到黑警既真面目，砌生豬肉、濫捕濫告既手段精彩絕倫，加上藍屍狗官蘇惠德。大家今時今日先醒悟當年既林子健有幾冤屈無助，只能說香港人進化太慢，子健走得太前<br />\n今日，香港全城仝人，我們都是林子健<br />\n對不起子健，我們來晚了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qRdLf79.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqRdLf79.jpg&h=b02529f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z23jkzQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz23jkzQ.jpg&h=0e09eabe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PPeB7eR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPPeB7eR.jpg&h=ce325a13&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mDEq0zR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmDEq0zR.jpg&h=9ebcc28c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 當年民主黨全黨都拋棄子健，得許智峰一個義無反顧撐手足撐到底，民主黨清泉 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7vUTUS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7vUTUS.jpg&h=311bc576&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b224b60cfc798a441bac21c5b4d5a5930bb4ce3","tid":1772221,"uid":209097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"以前邊有諗過會plan到咁完善黎屈你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b76a1cfb2a27712d3d5eb1e2502a295429e0c0","tid":1772221,"uid":174941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T12:20:30.000Z","msg":"128維園見"},{"pid":"84646802d3d24d6dc64d4a222fdda4325246aa13","tid":1772221,"uid":157483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b224b60cfc798a441bac21c5b4d5a5930bb4ce3","tid"